body.note: The following information applies to IBM Tealeaf version 9.0.2A only.
body.p:
IBM Tealeaf version 9.0.2A provides the same capabilities as version 9.0.2 and also includes the following additional capabilities:
Support for all common web page encodings, including those commonly used for Japanese, Chinese, and Korean encoded web pages.
Improved encoding, searching, filtering, and collation operations on non-ASCII data (characters outside of A-Z, a-z, 0-9, and common punctuation).
Support when the user data being processed is not the same as the native character encoding of the operating system. For example, Tealeaf components can process Arabic data on a French Windows operating system.
